.com%2F0VJxj7.gif&h=d795b37a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T06:28:23.000Z","msg":"5號係陳瑋嶸<br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181001/4de9645cb8c14380ac55d3ad69de35b5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20181001%2F4de9645cb8c14380ac55d3ad69de35b5.jpeg&h=b6140a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉松偉10號"}]}